{"tid":2291952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專業議政・梁繼昌：由始至終都係唔贊成制裁...","createTime":"2020-11-19T06:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T15:58:20.000Z","uid":273675,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c561e10000d013f113d54e84a54bd0a4a2a1dec","tid":2291952,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125533639_407646437283403_8336700527382503002_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=unvwlPUrADEAX-4graf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ccd40f0a51feaa7e9df7e7c3ee6e6ff4&amp;oe=5FDB9E4E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F125533639_407646437283403_8336700527382503002_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DunvwlPUrADEAX-4graf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dccd40f0a51feaa7e9df7e7c3ee6e6ff4%26oe%3D5FDB9E4E&h=a77307c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/photos/a.394935435221170/407646430616737/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkdinterview%2Fphotos%2Fa.394935435221170%2F407646430616737%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5kkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7165e37c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/photos/a.394935435221170/407646430616737/</a><br />\n前會計界議員、專業議政的梁繼昌於三月初應邀訪美，就有關「香港人權與民主法案」與美國官員交流，因而被指尋求境外勢力干預香港事務，即時喪失議員資格。<br />\n近日，梁繼昌接受本地媒體訪問時表示制裁對改善局勢根本無效，所以從不贊成；當日赴美是希望了解制裁機制如何運作，以減低一旦實行對香港的負面影響。<br />\n對於受普遍抗爭者所支持的「攬炒」概念，梁繼昌表示如「攬炒」是代表令香港變成一個欠活力、沒有外資的四線內地城市的話，是愚蠢但絕對不可能接受的「攬炒」。<br />\n<br />\n#梁繼昌 #專業議政 #民主派 #DQ風波 #第六屆立法會 #會計界 #功能組別 #攬炒 #制裁"},{"pid":"a536497042085f9bc3738f6a839abdd80246f910","tid":2291952,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"既得利益者唔贊成好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係我地呢啲無stake先成日想洗牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389f2e8c87fc02b9a37fcc4322b143ef3bcef12b","tid":2291952,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e80076c1414ace777068e1f8cadea3ae4c1b34","tid":2291952,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:04:48.000Z","msg":"波叔養了一頭犬，想做會計界議員"},{"pid":"f54c4b91d5ff40907d1c9691cbca2dedf3016700","tid":2291952,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbea56fcb3f3bafab5999df2b7fe1594fa3cea3","tid":2291952,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}